result.name: thermal-harrow-properties
result.notes: LiDAR derived polgons illustrating propeties within the Borough of Harrow with underlying thermal values and postcode data attached. Available in two file formats; primarily available as a Geography Markup Language (.gml) file with the schema (.XSD) being stored within the zipped file for the GML format. Also available to download as a shapefile (.shp) in the additional resources section.
result.title: Thermal Harrow Properties 2014
